* Desmonus didn't fail to notice BloodyStrikes optics traveling over her 
body as she stretched, glancing over towards Reptilica and seeing him do the 
same.
But then she turnes back and sees BloodyStrike nod.
Desmonus sees the annoyed look in BloodyStrikes face as he heard Reptilica 
answer too, a small smile turning her lips.
This could get interesting...and maybe she could get a free meal out of it 
as well.
She looked BloodyStrike over and then Reptilica. Dinner...and desert.

Desmonus nodds at BloodyStrikes introduction with an evil glint in her 
optics, her stomach growling just as the smell of his mech-fluid running 
through his veins.
She knew that he had some sort of thing for her, even if it was just because 
of her looks. But that was nothing more then she could have hoped for, two 
gullable males who would believe anything that cam out of her mouth...and 
maybe all she had to do was maintain a food source was keep them pleased.
A small price to pay for a full stomach.

She was just about to reach out and shake BloodyStrikes hand when Reptilica 
swatted his away and replaced it with his own.
But then she simply leaned back and crossed her arms for a moment, watching 
both of the bots fight over something or a nother...most likely her. Which 
would serve her purpose.

Desmonus simply sighed and then stepped forward, taking hold of each of 
their arms and then stepping in between them. Her voice more lighthearted 
then she felt.*

" Gentlemen, please.... You two both seem like you know this base from bolt 
to plating, and of course I'm new here so I don't really know my way around. 
Perhaps...a tour is in order?"
